UID is 100872341, i tried to get a record on pc but i made a mistake, is really not an isolated incident and very easily reproducible, just do this:

**1) **Go in story Acr 1  Chapter 6-8 (or any Myriam boss), with Aigis;
**2)** Go to the Myriam boss and exalt 4 times, using petrify as the 4°, then use the last exalt and her intention will change will still being petrified (is the same if aigis is the 5° one); 
**3)** She will still attack and lose the next round instead.   

You can test Uvhash in the same way, just petrify him right before triggering his strong attack when he reach the corresponding damage threshold to change his intention (i can't test it now).

For the Phase Change, just kill the first Phase of any boss while he is petrified and the effect will be nullified, then restart the battle and use petrify AFTER his intention has changed and is about to Phase change
